95FF">$value</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/class.gmagickpixel.php" class="type GmagickPixel" style="color:#EAB766">GmagickPixel</a></span></div>   }</div>  </div> </div> <h2>目录</h2><ul class="chunklist chunklist_reference"><li>{@link GmagickPixel::__construct} — The GmagickPixel constructor</li><li>{@link GmagickPixel::getcolor} — Returns the color</li><li>{@link GmagickPixel::getcolorcount} — Returns the color count associated with this color</li><li>{@link GmagickPixel::getcolorvalue} — Gets the normalized value of the provided color channel</li><li>{@link GmagickPixel::setcolor} — Sets the color</li><li>{@link GmagickPixel::setcolorvalue} — Sets the normalized value of one of the channels</li></ul></div>
