HT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-gmagickpixel.setcolor-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   The <span class="classname"><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/zh/class.gmagickpixel.php" class="classname">GmagickPixel</a></span> object.  </p> </div></div>
